This is a website about timekeeping system

Prerequisites
Python 3.12.x (recommended for compatibility)

Web Application
 - Activate the virtual environment (located at project root):
```# From the project root directory
.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1```
 - Set MONGO_CONNECTION_STRING and GEMINI_API_KEY to file .env
 - Install dependencies (if not already installed):`pip install -r requirements.txt`
 - Start the development server: `uvicorn app.main:app --reload`
 - The web application will be available at http://127.0.0.1:8000
